data.description: Fantastic Riverlakes home in Eagle Ranch with a Pool & PAID Solar! This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home is located close to the end of a cul-de-sac but near your favorite shops, golfing, dining and schools. Lovely great room floor plan features arched doorways, tile and wood laminate flooring, and plantation shutters and ceiling fans throughout. Great room is perfect for family gatherings with a corner fireplace and adjoining kitchen with stainless appliances, center island with seating, gas cooktop, and separate oven. Low maintenance backyard includes a refreshing in-ground swimming pool with raised deck and sheer descent waterfall, huge covered patio with four exterior ceiling fans,  fencing to secure the pool, and a small grass area. Perfect NW location for your family. Schedule a showing today!
